{"type":"message","id":"f88d5822","parentId":"ac121db0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:40:28.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know my workflow/process. Let me explain how I work.\n","thinkingSignature":"0dd2a31985402ebe42a827a157e02acd8b93e205766ffd1d0a01871790328900"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 简单！我的工作流程：\n\n**1️⃣ 你描述需求**\n告诉我想要什么——图像或视频，主题、风格、用途等\n\n**2️⃣ 我推荐方案**\n根据需求推荐最合适的模型和参数，默认用性价比最高的选项，同时告诉你价格\n\n**3️⃣ 优化提示词**\n我会把简单描述转化成高质量的生成提示，加入质量词、风格描述、镜头语言等\n\n**4️⃣ 生成 + 返回**\n调用 API 生成，完成后返回链接（图片直接返回，视频约 1-2 分钟）\n\n---\n\n**价格参考：**\n| 类型 | 最便宜 | 推荐 | 最高质量 |\n|------|--------|------|----------|\n| 图像 | Flux ¥0.01 | Flux ¥0.01 | Grok ¥0.10 |\n| 视频 | Kling-o1 ¥0.80 | Kling-o1 ¥0.80 | Kling-v2-6 ¥2.50 |\n\n---\n\n想生成什么？直接说你的想法就行 👇"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minim","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41704,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775792416041,"responseId":"0627a4213a36f276ca47e5121eb1ab2c"}}
