{"type":"message","id":"a6949457","parentId":"ba80872b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:41:49.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can do image-to-video generation. Yes, I can! According to my TOOLS.md:\n\n### 图生视频\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST https://proxy-roan-eight.vercel.app/api/generate \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"mode\": \"image-to-video\",\n    \"prompt\": \"缓慢平移镜头，微风拂动\",\n    \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/image.jpg\",\n    \"model\": \"kling-o1\",\n    \"duration\": 5\n  }' | jq -r '.jobId'\n```\n\nSo I can do image-to-video using kling-o1 (¥0.80) or other video models. \n\nNow I should give them a straightforward response about this capability.\n","thinkingSignature":"14827a1903b5095e9136dc776a015dc478c0d42cd33359c7aea13306aae68dc9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 可以！图生视频完全支持 🎬\n\n**使用方法：**\n1. 发一张参考图给我\n2. 告诉我想要的动作/场景\n3. 我用 Kling-o1（¥0.80 / 5秒）或 Kling-v2-6（¥2.50 / 更高质量）生成\n\n**Reference 模式**（角色一致性）：\n如果你有角色图，想让同一个角色做不同动作，用 Reference 模式 + Kling-v2-6（¥2.50），可以保持角色外观一致。\n\n---\n\n想试试吗？发图给我 + 描述动作就行 👇"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minim","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42120,"output":299,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42419,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775792490297,"responseId":"0627a46b31422ae3bedcdfaa66f37c38"}}
